data.jmetal

Class Experiments

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.jmetal.Experiments

  • public class Experiments
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will contain all the information related to the JMETAL framework. Will have all the 3 used variable types for JMETAL and will also be the main link between @see JMetalWorker and the JMetal's platform itself.

    skner
